snippet.title: Voxrush - Gameplay Trailer (Early Access)
snippet.description:
#Voxrush is available on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2057070/Voxrush

Voxrush is a time survival FPS game with a full destructible voxel environment.
Kill monsters, take points, upgrade stats and weapons, use skills and find a better way to survive as long as possible to become the best!
